{"tid":22694,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[長毛] 主人d 毛打kick 可以點做","createTime":"2016-12-04T14:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T05:59:50.000Z","uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"370109c902193ded91adaf790baeb5c1f46e5deb","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"屋企主人係長毛貓<br />\n其實已經一得閒就梳幾下<br />\n但肚個d 位 d 毛都係打哂kick<br />\n幫佢梳又梳唔到 佢又好掙扎梳到佢好痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩梳/方法 可以解到呢d 毛？<br />\n而家用緊d 好似人用既梳， 梳親佢 佢都好唔鐘意<br />\n唔知關唔關事呢？<br />\n上網睇話唔可以剪，但可以剃<br />\n如果自己買寵物用既剃刀 淨係幫佢剃走打結個d 毛，可唔可行呢？"},{"pid":"cf273c0f8136e5dbf8222ad8569dd6f42d041178","tid":22694,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"咩毛唔剪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb677727a1c69d1eb3894c832d8db871aa7b5e83","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩毛唔剪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇返黎 好似係怕剪到肉<br />\n不過其實我試過剪 但一剪佢就叫 <br />\n我怕佢痛就唔敢再剪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce883ec85395e3aa139e400626c138a247542d90","tid":22694,"uid":47681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:29:51.000Z","msg":"用手捉住個kick下面（近肉） 之後梳甩個kick佢就冇咁痛"},{"pid":"b8d17a27e8b612a64fb3f282f2e536a816d42b2d","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用手捉住個kick下面（近肉） 之後梳甩個kick佢就冇咁痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有咁做 但都解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一大力d 佢就走"},{"pid":"877d3a2ce4a1b5a5921556d497677750e8b3f96f","tid":22694,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5k642r7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5k642r7g&h=14964d6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69481e0509dc4d6a6eab9ddd7c5a10955b20bde5","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/5k642r7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5k642r7g&h=14964d6d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢把有咩特別咖？特別for 長毛貓？<br />\n而家用緊呢把 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1w64Xp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1w64Xp1.jpg&h=d4409636&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ae0190318868ea7d32cb74f33bfa2f7d5601f77","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"推下先。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c23649e8ba6fa328a070711fe4a8e5953bc7bd2","tid":22694,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/5k642r7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5k642r7g&h=14964d6d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢把有咩特別咖？特別for 長毛貓？<br />\n而家用緊呢把 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1w64Xp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1w64Xp1.jpg&h=d4409636&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢把梳長毛貓好洗好用，夠密，你果把要用密果邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9hxq7tz1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9hxq7tz1&h=48f27089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢隻要日日梳，唔係會kick"},{"pid":"59f0d1bd62e09a2332553dd3ae978c390b4af90c","tid":22694,"uid":47681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:30:25.000Z","msg":"上面勁密個把用緊梳頭頂，其餘用銀色個把會好d, 太密梳甩晒d毛"},{"pid":"37a2de1579b01395610ec5d9716e60e67a39fd0f","tid":22694,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxhmgv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxhmgv2.jpg&h=330467ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買把ed都唔係好貴姐..<br />\n或者圓個款<br />\n你用直排梳梳好似格硬扯甩佢 佢會痛架<br />\n唔大個結就可以用上面講個兩款梳擦鬆佢再梳走<br />\n或者用手由底「搣」開個結 再梳<br />\n大結唔貼肉就剪左佢 貼肉就最好用剷仔小心剷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望幫到你"},{"pid":"514fcbeffb458b565a0e81b0e9621b87127e2cc9","tid":22694,"uid":10047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:12:01.000Z","msg":"產青😁"},{"pid":"02cdc045f90834760a9911a3f5f3ae9ccb16c06b","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxhmgv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxhmgv2.jpg&h=330467ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買把ed都唔係好貴姐..<br />\n或者圓個款<br />\n你用直排梳梳好似格硬扯甩佢 佢會痛架<br />\n唔大個結就可以用上面講個兩款梳擦鬆佢再梳走<br />\n或者用手由底「搣」開個結 再梳<br />\n大結唔貼肉就剪左佢 貼肉就最好用剷仔小心剷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好 得閒就去買把呢d試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都追住佢幫佢梳毛 搞到佢都驚左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a90bb62759c52f4652a11d9cbc15c02e6cd883c","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>產青😁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剷左我怕主人唔認我呢個奴才<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0517169586e6a83aac3a9dd9b41d52695747c3c7","tid":22694,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/104458_53bb6a0e037569506b466098a9321ed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F104458_53bb6a0e037569506b466098a9321ed1.jpg&h=3dc99dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢款貴d 按摩梳 同上面我貼個款功用差唔多<br />\n不過e款真係比長毛貓狗用囉 上面我貼針梳個款平同多款貓狗都岩用<br />\n睇你自己選擇咁囉 如果你真係買可以到時再問人"},{"pid":"6e36ec6547d6ba8c3227e0fa9957e288631c47ae","tid":22694,"uid":6940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"火攻"},{"pid":"75f21563c84f052e1818d718628d0a19c3a0f583","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR3j6B1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR3j6B1.jpg&h=92e23347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d 除毛梳有冇用咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d 想買黎試下"},{"pid":"06c8df0cd8c5ef14e08d7c379c6dff5b62e494de","tid":22694,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR3j6B1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR3j6B1.jpg&h=92e23347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d 除毛梳有冇用咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d 想買黎試下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多死毛既貓狗就有用 <br />\n如果你個隻無咩死毛既話作用唔大<br />\n有都唔係用呢個梳日日梳 間唔中"},{"pid":"f0f55d2f4b8cd40cce28c89e6f6097d53e912928","tid":22694,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"日日梳毛應該唔洗用"},{"pid":"92de99e06b354cbe122e9c776eefb1f594f315e6","tid":22694,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"我都係用開耙型嗰隻勾梳。 <br />\n但重點係佢怕你搞個肚啲毛你用乜梳都係梳唔到。<br />\n我嗰隻都係好難梳肚仔毛，一梳就反抗，鬧人，走咗去。 但明明唔痛。 <br />\n所以我一定要用其他嘢去引開佢注意 線類繩類會比較好。 佢係咁扯條嘢同咬條嘢嗰陣就借機會梳佢個肚 。  <br />\n如果打咗結我都係用鏟毛鏟<br />\n如果唔係冬天會盡量鏟到啲毛打唔到結嘅長度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ecdwqfx9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fecdwqfx9&h=989ce423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b42cd71e71419551091d5427180e303e56a357e","tid":22694,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係用開耙型嗰隻勾梳。 <br />\n但重點係佢怕你搞個肚啲毛你用乜梳都係梳唔到。<br />\n我嗰隻都係好難梳肚仔毛，一梳就反抗，鬧人，走咗去。 但明明唔痛。 <br />\n所以我一定要用其他嘢去引開佢注意 線類繩類會比較好。 佢係咁扯條嘢同咬條嘢嗰陣就借機會梳佢個肚 。  <br />\n如果打咗結我都係用鏟毛鏟<br />\n如果唔係冬天會盡量鏟到啲毛打唔到結嘅長度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ecdwqfx9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fecdwqfx9&h=989ce423&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全就係咁！<br />\n一梳肚仔毛就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鏟毛方面有冇話邊部好d ？<br />\n<br />\n我隻衰野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">應該唔會有相認掛</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUaw9ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUaw9ef.jpg&h=ea097dce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e1e6c697a346d78f4c1168e5b973d5fd87b404d","tid":22694,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"針刷刷一刷，再用密齒梳慢慢梳，一定要用手按住d根位，否則好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n你手勢好可用較剪順毛削斷d結，當然把剪要利"},{"pid":"007979c6170434dc780635eff3904f32538eca44","tid":22694,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係用開耙型嗰隻勾梳。 <br />\n但重點係佢怕你搞個肚啲毛你用乜梳都係梳唔到。<br />\n我嗰隻都係好難梳肚仔毛，一梳就反抗，鬧人，走咗去。 但明明唔痛。 <br />\n所以我一定要用其他嘢去引開佢注意 線類繩類會比較好。 佢係咁扯條嘢同咬條嘢嗰陣就借機會梳佢個肚 。  <br />\n如果打咗結我都係用鏟毛鏟<br />\n如果唔係冬天會盡量鏟到啲毛打唔到結嘅長度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ecdwqfx9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fecdwqfx9&h=989ce423&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全就係咁！<br />\n一梳肚仔毛就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鏟毛方面有冇話邊部好d ？<br />\n<br />\n我隻衰野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">應該唔會有相認掛</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUaw9ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUaw9ef.jpg&h=ea097dce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nu<br />\n冇呀 我係用啲平貨鏟。不過同梳毛一樣 都係要引閻佢注意先鏟到 仲要追住佢通屋跑"}]}